data  plotdata <- clim_extract(locdata,a,b,c)"},{"path":"/articles/README.zh-CN.html","id":"walter-lieth的气候图绘制","dir":"Articles","previous_headings":"使用示例","what":"Walter & Lieth的气候图绘制","title":"climplot：用于绘制 Walter & Lieth 气候图的流程化工具","text":"以plotdata数据为例，导入到函数clim_plot中：  在上图中: 红色曲线代表气温的年际变化，蓝色曲线代表降水的年际变化。这两条曲线闭合形成了两种斑块，表示湿度和干燥程度。竖线填充的斑块代表湿润季节，散点填充的斑块代表干旱季节。与降水曲线颜色相同的多边形表示降水量大于100mm的月份，表示雨季。 左上角的信息包括名称、海拔高度和位置坐标。右上方为年平均气温和年平均降水量。","code":"data(\"plotdata\") loc <- subset(plotdata,No==2) clim_plot(loc)"},{"path":"/articles/README.zh-CN.html","id":"其他参考","dir":"Articles","previous_headings":"","what":"其他参考","title":"climplot：用于绘制 Walter & Lieth 气候图的流程化工具","text":"更多参考内容请阅读软件包内的帮助文件，以及vignettes中的信息。","code":""},{"path":"/articles/README.zh-CN.html","id":"参考文献","dir":"Articles","previous_headings":"","what":"参考文献","title":"climplot：用于绘制 Walter & Lieth 气候图的流程化工具","text":"Guijarro J (2023). climatol: Climate Tools (Series Homogenization Derived Products), 4.0.0., https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=climatol. Fick, S.E. R.J. Hijmans, (2017). WorldClim 2: new 1km spatial resolution climate surfaces global land areas. International Journal Climatology 37 (12): 4302-4315. Harris, ., Osborn, T.J., Jones, P.D., Lister, D.H. (2020). Version 4 CRU TS monthly high-resolution gridded multivariate climate dataset. Scientific Data 7: 109. Walter H & Lieth H (1960): Klimadiagramm Weltatlas. G. Fischer, Jena.","code":""},{"path":"/authors.html","id":null,"dir":"","previous_headings":"","what":"Authors","title":"Authors and Citation","text":"Auman Chan. Maintainer.","code":""},{"path":"/authors.html","id":"citation","dir":"","previous_headings":"","what":"Citation","title":"Authors and Citation","text":"Chan (2023). climplot: climplot: Facilitate tailor Walter & Lieth climatic diagram drawing. R package version 0.2.1, https://github.com/auman-chan/climplot.","code":"@Manual{,   title = {climplot: climplot: Facilitate and tailor Walter & Lieth climatic diagram drawing},   author = {Auma