e":""},{"path":"/reference/climate_data.html","id":"ref-usage","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Usage","title":"Obtain climate data for climatic diagram construction — clim_extract","text":"","code":"clim_extract(file,mintemp_path=NA,maxtemp_path=NA, prec_path=NA,Frost=FALSE,exmintemp_path=NA)"},{"path":"/reference/climate_data.html","id":"arguments","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Arguments","title":"Obtain climate data for climatic diagram construction — clim_extract","text":"file data.frame(see details dataset locdata) following 5 columns: : Serial number locations location: Abbreviation locations lon: Longitude locations decimal digit (West longitude represented negative numbers) lat: Latitude locations decimal digit (South latitude represented negative numbers) altitude: Altitude locations columns information allowed behind columns     discarded following process. mintemp_path path folder annual average minimum temperature. folder contains 12 .tif files corresponding data 12 months. maxtemp_path path folder annual average maximum temperature. folder contains 12 .tif files corresponding data 12 months. prec_path path folder annual average maximum temperature. folder contains 12 .tif files corresponding data 12 months. Frost logical value whether calculate annual extreme minimum temperature,follow-plotting frost months. Default FALSE. exmintemp_path path folder annual extreme minimum temperature. folder contains 12 .tif files corresponding data 12 months.","code":""},{"path":"/reference/climate_data.html","id":"value","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Value","title":"Obtain climate data for climatic diagram construction — clim_extract","text":"data.frame annual average precipitation, annual average minimum temperature annual average max temperature 12 months, well essential information every location. Frost=True, also include values annual extreme minimum    temperature plotting forsty months. ,location,lon,lat: Information locations,parameter file. type: labels climate data, encompassing annual average precipitation,     annual average minimum temperature annual average maximum temperature.     event Frost=True, also incorporate annual extreme minimum temperature. 1-12: column names particular climate data type     correspond monthly values ranging January December. See details dataset plotdata.","code":""},{"path":"/reference/climate_data.html","id":"details","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Details","title":"Obtain climate data for climatic diagram construction — clim_extract","text":"function extracts precipitation temperature series arranged climate data RasterLayer format, arranges data frame plotting climatic diagram. RasterLayer computed Worldclim Historical monthly weather data 2010-2019 (Version 2.5 minutes,https://worldclim.org/data/monthlywth.html), containing annual average precipitation, annual average minimum temperature annual average max temperature 12 months across 2010-2019. can output original climate data mentioned running code script /clim_cal.R, download directly supplementary material.","code":""},{"path":"/reference/climate_data.html","id":"references","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"References","title":"Obtain climate data for climatic diagram construction — clim_extract","text":"Guijarro J (2023). climatol: Climate Tools (Series Homogenization Derived Products), 4.0.0., https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=climatol.Fick, S.E. R.J. Hijmans, (2017). WorldClim 2: new 1km spatial resolution climate surfaces global land areas. International Journal Climatology 37 (12): 4302-4315.Harris, ., Osborn, T.J., Jones, P.D., Lister, D.H. (2020). Version 4 CRU TS monthly high-resolution gridded multivariate climate dataset. Scientific Data 7: 109.Walter H & Lieth H (1960): Klimadiagramm Weltatlas. G. Fischer, Jena.","code":""},{"path":"/reference/climate_data.html","id":"ref-examples","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"E